## How to Use This File

The engine reads this file before writing any article. It uses competitor analysis to:
- Identify content gaps you can fill
- Avoid producing articles that merely repeat what already ranks
- Find angles, data points, and formats that competitors miss
- Set a quality bar: your article must be meaningfully better than the top 5

When auto-generated, the engine populates this by analyzing the top 10 SERP results for each target keyword.

